# Render / Netlify / Vercel static-site rewrite rules.
#
# Open House Report public share links live at https://openhousecopilot.com/r/{token}
# but are actually served by the FastAPI backend at
# https://openhouseboss-api.onrender.com/r/{token}. This rewrite forwards
# the request (status=200 = transparent rewrite, NOT a redirect — the
# browser stays on openhousecopilot.com and Open Graph link previews
# unfurl with the pretty domain).
/r/*  https://openhouseboss-api.onrender.com/r/:splat  200
